---
import { EncryptedText } from "../ui/encrypted-text";
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="mb-16">
      <span class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent font-medium">
        <EncryptedText client:visible text="MISSION" />
      </span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-near-black leading-tight mb-12">
      Developing the Next Generation of National Security Innovators
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
      <p class="text-dark-gray leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
        SJSU NSIN brings together students from engineering, computer science, policy, and business to tackle real national security challenges. Located in the heart of Silicon Valley, we occupy a unique position at the crossroads of cutting-edge technology and the defense ecosystem — giving our members unparalleled access to the people and problems shaping the future of national security.
      </p>
      <p class="text-dark-gray leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
        Our approach is hands-on: we connect students directly with defense industry partners and government agencies to work on real-world problems. Through speaker events, hackathons, externships, and policy discussions, we build the workforce pipeline that national security demands — training students who can think critically, build rapidly, and operate at the intersection of technology and strategy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-l-2 border-accent pl-8 py-4">
      <p class="font-mono text-lg md:text-xl text-near-black leading-relaxed">
        "At the intersection of Silicon Valley and national security, the next breakthrough is waiting."
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
